Paper: hep-th/0212148

Date: 2002-12-13

Title: Comment on 'Interaction of global and local monopoles'

Authors: A. Achucarro, J. Urrestilla

Comments: 3 pages, 1 figure, uses REVTEX4

We point out a problem with the stability of composite (global-magnetic)monopoles recently proposed by J. Spinelly, U. de Freitas and E.R. Bezerra deMello [Phys. Rev. D66, 024018 (2002)].